description: Reinflate your burst tires after running over a spike strip.
longDescription: Instantly reinflate your burst tires after running over a spike strip during a Pursuit.

description: Using this during a Race sends traffic cars into the leader.
longDescription: Using this during a Race redirects traffic cars into the race leader"s path.

description: Instantly end a Pursuit when you are in Cooldown.
longDescription: Instantly end a Pursuit by playing this Powerup when you are in Cooldown mode.
Use the Shield to protect yourself against the Traffic Magnet Powerup.

description: Catch the leaders with a burst of speed.
longDescription: Boosts your car"s performance when you are in 2nd place or lower.

description: Ready all Powerups for immediate use.
longDescription: Resets the timer on all Powerups so you can use them again instantly.

description: Knock cars out of the way with ramming speed.
longDescription: Choose Juggernaut when you want to drive through traffic; not round it.

description: Push Cops away from you to get a better chance to escape.
longDescription: Use this Powerup to push Cops away from you and give you a better chance to escape.

description: Triggers an Emergency Evade for your entire team
longDescription: Triggers an Emergency Evade for your entire team

description: Increase your speed to catch up to the leader or escape the cops.
longDescription: Increases your speed briefly to help catch up to the leader or escape the Cops

description: Adds another lap to a multiple-lap Race. Usable only once per Race.
longDescription: Adds another lap to a multiple-lap Race (like Circuit) but it can only be used once per Race.

description: Gives your team a short boost in speed.
longDescription: Gives your team a short boost in speed.
